snippet.title: \SPEK.TAKL\ - Banned Edition - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
\SPEK.TAKL\ is an intense, intimate and disturbing horror-themed psychosexual exploration on the lengths some of us go to in order to avoid facing the inevitable. It is the late-night television watching simulator that was banned on gaming's most popular platform, now available UNCENSORED in an exciting new director's cut.

To download and play : 
https://somewhat.itch.io/spektakl-banned
